OL,3,CTeenager campaigns for better safety
OL,4,Cafter being left in school during fire
OL,6,FWhile other pupils at Hyde High School
OL,7,Fwere evacuated, Lucas was told to stay
OL,8,Fput.
OL,10,FSpeaking on ITV's Good Morning
OL,11,FBritain, Lucas recalled the incident
OL,12,Fand said: "I was petrified.
OL,14,F"I started to smell smoke and because
OL,15,Fof my disability, I was worried about
OL,16,Fmy immune system. If I got smoke into
OL,17,Fmy lungs, who knows what would happen?"
