OL,3,CTeenager campaigns for better safety
OL,4,Cafter being left in school during fire
OL,6,FLucas said: "After it happened, I
OL,7,Fresearched the current legislation and
OL,8,FI was shocked to see that schools
OL,9,Fdon't have evac chairs.
OL,11,F"They might be costly but you can't
OL,12,Fput a price on my life, or other
OL,13,Fpeople's."
OL,15,FHis petition, _NoStudentLeftBehind, is
OL,16,Fgaining support and Lucas says he is
OL,17,Fdetermined no disabled student will
OL,18,Fever be left waiting in fear again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
