OL,3,CTeenager campaigns for better safety
OL,4,Cafter being left in school during fire
OL,6,FLucas is working with the Emergency
OL,7,FGroup, a collective of emergency
OL,8,Fresponse companies that provide life-
OL,9,Fsaving emergency equipment including
OL,10,Fevacuation chairs and defibrillators.
OL,12,FThe group donated four evacuation
OL,13,Fchairs to his school is supporting his
OL,14,Fcampaign for safer and more accessible
OL,15,Fschools.
OL,17,F"The reaction to the campaign has been
OL,18,Famazing." Lucas said.
OL,20,F"Together, we can make a difference."
